  <lyrics>[V1]
 
. G       C    G            D  G
 Love divine, all loves ex-cel-ling,
. C                 G    D7   G
 Joy of heav’n to earth come down; ||
. G      C   G          B/D# Em
 Fix in us thy humble dwell-ing;
. C        G        D       G
 All thy faithful mercies crown!||
. Em    Em/B  B   Em     B
 Jesus, Thou art all compassion,
. G       C/G  G  D/A    A   D7      
 Pure un-bound-ed love Thou art; ||
. G     C   G          B/D# Em
 Visit us with Thy sal-va-tion;
. C      G     D7        G
 Enter every trembling heart.
 
 
[V2]
. G           C      G          D  G 
 Breathe, O breathe Thy loving Spirit,
. C          G   D7    G
 Into every troubled breast! ||
. G      C  G          B/D# Em
 Let us all in Thee in-he-rit;
. C       G         D       G
 Let us find that promised rest.||
. Em    Em/B B    Em       B
 Take a-way the love of sinning;
. G    C/G  G D/A A  D7      
 Alpha and O-me-ga be; ||
. G       C        G    B/D# Em
 End of faith, as its Beginning,
. C       G         D7  G
 Set our hearts at liberty.
 
 
[V3]
. G        C    G       D  G
 Come, Al-migh-ty to de-li-ver,
. C               G    D7  G
 Let us all Thy life receive; ||
. G        C   G     B/D# Em
 Suddenly return and never,
. C      G        D       G
 Never more Thy temples leave.||
. Em     Em/B  B   Em      B
 Thee we would be always blessing,
. G        C/G  G  D/A    A  D7      
 Serve Thee as Thy hosts above, ||
. G          C    G            B/D# Em
 Pray and praise Thee without ceasing,
. C     G       D7      G
 Glory in Thy perfect love.
 
 
[V4]
. G       C     G          D  G
 Finish, then, Thy new cre-a-tion;
. C                 G   D7  G
 Pure and spotless let us be. ||
. G      C   G         B/D# Em
 Let us see Thy great salvation
. C     G      D        G
 Perfectly restored in Thee;||
. Em         Em/B  B   Em   B
 Changed from glo-ry into glory,
. G       C/G   G   D/A   A   D7      
 Till in heav’n we take our place, ||
. G        C   G            B/D#  Em
 Till we cast our crowns before Thee,
. C        G      D7        G
 Lost in wonder, love, and praise.
</lyrics>
